<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/28424010">用领结 、盆栽 、打火机、剑、这几个物件能写出怎样的故事？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3552257" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content"></div>


